title: Musée d’Orsay Reveals NFT Auction Tied to Historic On-Chain Exhibition
description: Five NFTs, collectively called “The Convergence of Breath,” will go on sale Thursday as a part of the museum’s “Code d’Orsay” exhibition.

title: Webull ended crypto offerings due to SEC opposition during past IPO attempts
description:
Online brokerage Webull decided to cut its crypto offerings because of the unfavorable regulatory landscape in the US as it waits for approval to list on Nasdaq via a special purpose acquisition company (SPAC), Bloomberg News reported on Feb. 28. The company said that its previous attempt to carry out an initial public offering (IPO) […]
